			(property "Description" "The IDT F2912 is a high reliability, low insertion loss 50 SPDT (SP2T) absorptive RF switch designed for a multitude of wireless and other RF applications. This device covers a broad frequency range from 0.009 MHz to 9000 MHz. In addition to providing low insertion loss, the F2912 also delivers excellent linearity and isolation performance while providing 50 ohm terminations to the unused RF input port.The F2912 uses a single positive supply voltage of 3.3V supporting three states using either 3.3 V or 1.8"
				(at 0 0 0)
				(effects
